  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/2d7cb4a2fba80be16c2e7c40064e6442.avif?t=1712768175\" width=580 height=900 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>THE ROBOTS HAVE REBELLED!</strong><br>Shoot, survive and defend as an armored vehicle against a rebellious swarm of robots. Pick up what was once known as floppy disks to gather knowledge and experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/c3395f07b79f88da94b3be6bf087a995.poster.avif?t=1712768175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/c3395f07b79f88da94b3be6bf087a995.webm?t=1712768175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/c3395f07b79f88da94b3be6bf087a995.mp4?t=1712768175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>WEAPONS WITH SPECIALIZATIONS</strong><br>Choose from a vast collection of upgrades and weapons, each with their own specializations and perks. <br>Unlock a selection of vehicles and traits for unique and diverse gameplay experiences.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/8720cb8836e9ce3af4d9d91dc9b43484.poster.avif?t=1712768175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/8720cb8836e9ce3af4d9d91dc9b43484.webm?t=1712768175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/8720cb8836e9ce3af4d9d91dc9b43484.mp4?t=1712768175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>DUNGEON AND MAP CHALLENGES</strong><br>Discover and explore factories for extra loot, but beware of the increasing danger and challenges lying behind those entries.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/bea670be7cd35c1304a9548a796cc514.poster.avif?t=1712768175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/bea670be7cd35c1304a9548a796cc514.webm?t=1712768175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/bea670be7cd35c1304a9548a796cc514.mp4?t=1712768175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 different vehicles with diverse behavior - and more to come!<br></li><li>More than 21 unique weapons and upgrades.<br></li><li>Obtain bonus effects by mixing and matching traits.<br></li><li>Fast paced, casual bullet hell shooter.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>THE ROBOTS HAVE REBELLED!</strong><br>Shoot, survive and defend as an armored vehicle against a rebellious swarm of robots. Pick up what was once known as floppy disks to gather knowledge and experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/c3395f07b79f88da94b3be6bf087a995.poster.avif?t=1712768175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/c3395f07b79f88da94b3be6bf087a995.webm?t=1712768175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/c3395f07b79f88da94b3be6bf087a995.mp4?t=1712768175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>WEAPONS WITH SPECIALIZATIONS</strong><br>Choose from a vast collection of upgrades and weapons, each with their own specializations and perks. <br>Unlock a selection of vehicles and traits for unique and diverse gameplay experiences.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/8720cb8836e9ce3af4d9d91dc9b43484.poster.avif?t=1712768175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/8720cb8836e9ce3af4d9d91dc9b43484.webm?t=1712768175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/8720cb8836e9ce3af4d9d91dc9b43484.mp4?t=1712768175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>DUNGEON AND MAP CHALLENGES</strong><br>Discover and explore factories for extra loot, but beware of the increasing danger and challenges lying behind those entries.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/bea670be7cd35c1304a9548a796cc514.poster.avif?t=1712768175\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/bea670be7cd35c1304a9548a796cc514.webm?t=1712768175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2025930/extras/bea670be7cd35c1304a9548a796cc514.mp4?t=1712768175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 different vehicles with diverse behavior - and more to come!<br></li><li>More than 21 unique weapons and upgrades.<br></li><li>Obtain bonus effects by mixing and matching traits.<br></li><li>Fast paced, casual bullet hell shooter.</li></ul>",
